      <link>//localhost:1313/about/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>//localhost:1313/about/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;about&#34;&gt;&#xA;  About&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#about&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Hi there! 👋&lt;br&gt;&#xA;My name is Dylan.&lt;br&gt;&#xA;I am a student studying Information Technology at Wellington Institute of Technology in New Zealand. 🎉&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;what-i-do&#34;&gt;&#xA;  What I do&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#what-i-do&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;I am currently taking the following courses for Trimester 1:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Discrete Mathematics&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Information Security II&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Linux System Administration&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Responsive Web Design&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;soft-skills&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Soft Skills&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#soft-skills&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Teaching&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Communication&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Problem-solving&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Critical thinking&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Leadership&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;technical-skills&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Technical Skills&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#technical-skills&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Languages: JavaScript, CSS, Java, C, C#, Bash, Python&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Software: VScode, NeoVim, Git/GitHub, Obsidian&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Operating Systems: Arch Linux, Kali Linux, Proxmox, Debian/Fedora-based systems&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;main-fields-of-interest&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Main Fields of Interest&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#main-fields-of-interest&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;I enjoy building and setting up Servers and Computers. 🖥️&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Another interest of mine is Home labbing where I have a home server running Proxmox.&lt;br&gt;&#xA;You can find more information on my homelab &lt;a href=&#34;https://dylantaylor.net/projects/#homelab&#34;  class=&#34;external-link&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;I also enjoy hacking (ethically of course) and doing CTF challenges (notably NZCSC 2023 where my team came 20th in the country).&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;outside-of-it-and-polytech&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Outside of IT and Polytech&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#outside-of-it-and-polytech&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;When I am not working on any University or Personal projects I like to:&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
